{
  "texts": [
    "As depicted in Figure 4(b), the accuracy of MetaRAG improves progressively as the maximum iteration count increases.",
    "However, once the iteration count reaches 5, the performance peaks, indicating that deeper metacognitive reflection can indeed enhance inference accuracy.",
    "Nevertheless, excessively increasing the number of reflection rounds leads to a slight decline in results.",
    "This could be attributed to the model's diminishing ability to extract more useful information or suggestions through the metacognitive mechanism.",
    "An intriguing observation is a minor accuracy peak at an iteration count of 2."
  ]
}